{"tid":1992650,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真正人肉流動連農牆=> 貼士跑步號碼牌","createTime":"2020-04-28T09:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T13:53:12.000Z","uid":259520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f5421332de5f6f07f9d97afdd8ed1f790b9a7f","tid":1992650,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"真正人肉流動連農牆=&gt; 貼士跑步號碼牌<br />\n<br />\n將單一文宣print出來,然後好似跑步號碼牌扣在 T恤或衫上.<br />\n<br />\n1) 重點選定一日先作宣傳為人肉流動連農牆日.(唔好太急,有時間做宣傳.)<br />\n2) 預先選定幾張至十幾張文宣.(讓人自己print,同派發)<br />\na) 不要多字(4-8個字易見)<br />\nb) 不要血腥侮辱(避免犯法)<br />\nc) 可以既盡量以漫畫表達<br />\n3) 點解要選定一日,可以集中人數去做.如果個別人士單一去做.<br />\n人少容易給警方玩.<br />\n人多參與,政府同共狗唔知點應對.<br />\n(唔係P牌,見沉幫開新post,如認為有意義)"},{"pid":"6d0ce42c39cb2c760a7db86cca005c7cefe8b3ed","tid":1992650,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"我日日著緊721 TEE<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8e5f5304e30b6086aee58d1be13d00d113f07b","tid":1992650,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:34:25.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"837723fadf405afade10cd744334615e5963a7dc","tid":1992650,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"81e30f2a4e4731dc464dd485e000f19d93d9cc85","tid":1992650,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}